title: Bubble-Bobble 390 KB!!!
description:
A proper golden oldie for you here a game from 1989


The first of the puzzle bobble series which is a cute little platformer where you play as a little lizard thing and you shoot bubbles at enemies

Really fun game to play i think you should try its only 390kb, but you must use dosbox to run this game.

If any of you think this is a virus becuase of the size i assure you it isnt its just becuase the game was made in 1989 (golden oldie) is why its so small.

Enjoy
